section_label: Three images showing different angles of the multi
raw_md_fragment:
[IMAGE]
Three images showing different angles of the multifamily building. The first image shows the side of the building with a narrow alleyway. The second image shows the rear parking area with several cars. The third image focuses on the utility meters attached to the side of the building.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with brick walls and mailboxes on the right side. The stairwell has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a hallway with a wooden door and a painting on the wall. The floor is carpeted, and there is a metal railing.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a brick building exterior with multiple windows and air conditioning units. There is a pathway leading to a double-door entrance with a red awning.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with a painting on the wall. The stairwell has carpeted steps and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]
